# Git + Instruqt publish

When you finish changes under `instruqt/` (especially `instruqt/elastic-adaptive-metrics/` or bundled `track_scripts`), **before ending the task**:

1. Commit any outstanding changes with a clear message.
2. **`git push`** from the repo root (`origin`).
3. **`instruqt track push --force`** from `instruqt/elastic-adaptive-metrics/` (same directory as that track’s `track.yml`).

Confirm both commands succeed; report the track manage URL if Instruqt prints it.
